http://java.sun.com/products/jdk/1.2/docs/api/java/text/SimpleDateFormat.html

Proposed HREF:
http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4.2/docs/api/java/text/SimpleDateFormat.html

Done in HEAD and ANT_16_BRANCH.
